*","contents":"I love capcut, I’ve been using this app since August (of 2024) and 4 months later, (December 2024) I’ve been having issues with this app. \nFirst, in the app u literally have to pay for capcut pro, which is fine, but the prices are pretty high. Like I know they do like 65% off, but I don’t know if that’s helping as much. In my opinion, I personally think Capcut is money hungry. Second, the storage issue, I ended up deleting all my videos and edits for storage and deleted many apps for that storage, and it still says I need to delete my storage in order to use capcut and edit on there, I restarted my phone and that worked but 5 minutes later it just get worse. I hope capcut that u fix that issue. The good part about capcut is that it’s free, there are many options to choose for your edits, and you can watch templates but the bad side of templates is that some content creators post Inappropriate and disturbing for many people. This app is 12+ who the heck wants to watch people in weird outfits showing off there body like what the sigma. I can’t even let my 9 year old sister to watch templates it’s like tiktok but u can use the templates like who wants to use those green screens that are too inappropriate? Not me for sure, and when I reported them nothings happened it’s like people like watching and using that cringeness. There should be controls on what u should watch because that is just cringe…. Overall I rate capcut 3 stars.","rating":5,"reviewerName":"Izzyehh","dateAuthorText":"* null * · Izzyehh"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"11565603987","title":"I love this app but…","date":"2024-08-03T01:08:46.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"Well, when I go into Camera, there is no more make up a.k.a. the fairy, the make up, and stuff. I don’t know if people have been using them badly and that is why you took them off, or it is just a bug. I have been wanting to use them for so long but they’re gone. So, I have been wondering, if you will check it out, or you purposely took them off. Also, a lot of other stuff has been getting taken off. Again, if you can take a look, that would be great, or if you purposely took them off I am perfectly fine with that. Just warning you. Also when for some reason I deleted this app and got it back I look for all my templates and videos I made but they aren’t showing up. I tried everything I signed into my account but it still didn’t work. I am extremely sad because I usually don’t save all my important templates or videos because I don’t want to take up storage but now I don’t even have them. I also read some other reviews and some other people are having this problem. Please get to this problem. It seems that you are ignoring all the reviews if you are not, and you are reading this, please do something about this. Also, whenever I make some certain videos, it says that the part of the video was deleted, but I didn’t delete any part of the video so now the important parts of my video are gone, the funny parts, the sad parts and maybe boring parts that are still wanted. I really hope that you can get to this because I lost some of my very important videos parts of my important videos and some filters. Hope you can get to this. Thank you.","rating":5,"reviewerName":"wow lots of nicknames","dateAuthorText":"* null * · wow lots of nicknames"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"11685570159","title":"STOP MAKING EVERYTHING PRO!","date":"2024-09-03T20:13:59.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"I rater this high, only because I do think the app is very good for editing. I just hate how they keep adding things to pro. I will not pay 100 dollars just to have one feature I used to be able to have. I don’t want to have to switch over to a different app, but if I have to, I very much will. It makes me very angry to see such simple things such as “SMOOTH SLOW MOTION” turn into a pro feature. I can take a video in my camera roll and edit a part to be slow motion for free, so why does it need to be paid for in CapCut? There is no reason for everything needing to be paid for when they are such simple things. I understand the more advanced features being pro, but seriously? Slow motion? Seriously? I would appreciate if you guys actually read this review and realized how many people are frustrated by the amount of things turning into pro features. And another thing, the hashtags. Trying to search something is painful because the only thing showing up is two items of what you actually searched and about a hundred ads or things that just have a high amount of likes. If I want to search and find something that I saw WITH THE HASHTAG I would like if it actually showed up when I go to look for it again. Please fix this. And please stop making so many features pro, it’s really frustrating as a person that isn’t even making money from this and only using this app for fun. I don’t even have an account, I simple wanted to use CapCut to make edits for fun, and if I have to, I will switch to Alight motion. Please read and consider this.","rating":5,"reviewerName":"Pizza4U&Me","dateAuthorText":"* null * · Pizza4U&Me"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"12156958934","title":"This is why I love CapCut so much","date":"2025-01-07T20:27:04.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"Is an amazing app it’s the best app possible if you want to edit videos if you want to have videos for show if you want to add videos too you can make your own edit by just trying. I know it doesn’t look very nice. I know it doesn’t look cute but in my opinion, I read five stars is not the best app, but it actually is the best app you can make your own videos. That’s really good. I wanna make my own videos but if you wanna edit videos, you wanna edit the photos cause it doesn’t look right CapCut video editor and it’s in the picture. Editor is the best app for like constant on TikTok. I didn’t even know about CapCut. I heard it from TikTok but it’s an amazing app is the best app. I love this app so much in the creator of CapCut. I hope you read this. I love CapCut so much. I’m reading at five stars but if you look at it and you see it and if you like it, I’ll want you to read a five stars. I’m based on my life review. You would want to see it and visit it out because you say I read at five stars and my title is this is why I love CapCut so much. And it’ll be so fun and you can go like I always wanted a brother I always wanted a sister. I always want a cousin just like you. I always wanted to mama I always wanted a dad just like you like it’s so fun. I love this app and I love everything like about this app like I can’t even explain it because I’m so happy so write this for you. This is the best review ever all of apps. Love you and I hope you make More. Have a nice day.","rating":5,"reviewerName":"The gvj,gmtyf","dateAuthorText":"* null * · The gvj,gmtyf"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"10675478055","title":"I LOVE CAPCUT!!!!!","date":"2023-12-09T18:51:40.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"Like the title says, I love CapCut. It’s absolutely just so amazing, and you can make millions of things in CapCut. If you’re video maker, or are just there for the templates, there’s something for everyone. However, there are a few things that kind of ruin my experience.\nThe first being CapCut Pro. I want to use CapCut freely, without being constantly nagged about something that costs $8 a month, or $75 yearly. The most awful thing about CapCut Pro is the fact that some of my favorite transitions and animations have been added to CapCut Pro, so I can no longer use them. \nAnother thing that ruins my experience is a bug. I think it was accidentally added in a recent update, because this is new for me. When going through photos and videos in CapCut, like choosing which ones to add to my video, some of the items will be black, like the item is just flat out black, with how long the video is still showing, but I’m still able to add to add it to my video. As a GachaTuber, this is a ginormous issue because in order to make the videos that I make, I need to take countless screenshots and put them into the editing app. If I can’t see what the photos are, it adds to my storage trying to take more photos, hoping that they will show up, and lessens my patience and motivation. \nOverall, I absolutely love CapCut and I encourage any and all types of video making in this app. I only hope that the bugs will get fixed and removed so that I can easily keep making videos.","rating":4,"reviewerName":"rainbowunipuppy","dateAuthorText":"* null * · rainbowunipuppy"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"10467054641","title":"😳Highly😳 recommend😳","date":"2023-10-12T20:09:59.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"This app has so many edits and so many reasons why you should get this app. This app is great quality the filters and the editing is top notch. There’s also so many filters and edits to choose from. This is like my favorite app out of all my apps I have! I chose to download this app is because it just makes my photos and videos look like really cool and look amazing, for all the people that’s out there I would get this app I can literally change your life and I have been using this app for as long as I can remember to be quite honest my old phone used to have nothing but CapCut videos that I make. CapCut 🪩is just like a really entertaining app! I like about it is that there’s no ads and free edits that you can just chose and not even have to do it yourself this is like a really chill fun entertainment app. There’s also a VIP or like other people call it a free upgrade, but it does cost money and you can cancel at any time. For me, I think CapCut is a amazing app to be quite honest. Mostly every thing is free when it comes to editing like FX 🛸or free scissors cutting photo is free. Mostly everything is free but for me I just like to make lots of really cool, amazing videos, but my favorite part is about making my editing is to put like sparkling in my video to make it a little. More cooler. 👻🫧So I would highly recommend getting this app. It can Change your life 🤓it could change every video and photo that you have CapCut is basically one of the most favorite apps that anybody has ever got! ITS OUT OF THIS WORLD 🌎","rating":5,"reviewerName":"Allie childers","dateAuthorText":"* null * · Allie childers"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"12089644994","title":"Fix this please","date":"2024-12-21T18:04:29.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"I love capcut and think it is a great app to make plenty of fun videos with friends on, but there is one minor issue I was wondering capcut can fix. \n\nSo there’s this cool option to REVERSE a video on CapCut, where you can throw something behind you, reverse it, and look like you’re catching an object that just appeared in midair without even looking behind you. It’s pretty cool, but sometimes it glitches - and by sometimes, I mean 65% of the time, and if I’m honest, it can be pretty annoying. For example, I put in a cool video of me doing a throw-back thing with my friend a few days ago, but when I went to reverse it, it reversed a completely different video than what I wanted to reverse - a random one from my camera roll I haven’t seen in ages, and it makes me scared because I don’t want CapCut to have access to my whole camera roll, because I have some private things in there. Plus, it’s just plain annoying, because I tried to reverse the video several times but the app wouldn’t do it and I got the feeling it was just REFUSING to do it, and I wondered why and how it could do that. It didn’t give me a reason why it wouldn’t do that - no notification or little alert saying it was too short or too long or too dark or too bright or something like that. If possible, I’d like to creators of CapCut and come back to fix that, because it is just plain obnoxious how it  usually doesn’t work. Other than that, great work on the app, and I love CapCut very much.","rating":4,"reviewerName":"Just a girl in CT","dateAuthorText":"* null * · Just a girl in CT"},{"$kind":"Review","id":"13756807278","title":"Great app. But….","date":"2026-02-16T21:01:12.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"As a CapCut user, this app is amazing, their templates for Slomo, velocity, and entertainment videos are on point, giving children a slight preview of TikTok (as it is made by the creators of). but I wish that there not so many inappropriate and suggestive material. There are a lot of people suggesting things on what to bring to run away, suicídě topics, r@pist stories, and a lot of AI related content. Please fix this to keep people safe. And if parents are looking at this and you approve of the app, make sure you preview what your child is watching/ making with templates but also give them some privacy. Again this app is amazing, it just has things to keep note. CapCut, maybe you could add a restrictions setting for parents? (5 stars so you could see this message.)\nAccording to their privacy policy, they collect content, associated metadata, and user generated content. SO BE CAREFUL WHAT YOU POST/ EXPORT, THEY CAN SEE IT. When I was younger, I used to always use CapCut for Slomo videos of my horses, but then all of the sudden CapCut became moneybags. They’ve created a thing called “Pro” that states “easy cancellation” when in reality, IT IS A NIGHTMARE TO CANCEL. And there is also a problem their customer support. ITS LIKE THERE IS NO CUSTOMER SUPPORT (this issue is stated multiple times by other users in reviews). I did not write this to accuse CapCut of anything, I want to keep other people and kids safe from the bad stuff in this app.","rating":5,"reviewerName":"Please see this immediately","dateAuthorText":"* null * · Please see this immediately","response":{"$kind":"Response","id":"59689922","contents":"Your feedback is valuable to us. We will record your feedback to the development team to optimize the product. Thank you for your feedback.","date":"2026-02-18T10:49:16.000Z","dateText":"* null *"}}],"url":nul