. I really hope that you can get to this because I lost some of my very important videos parts of my important videos and some filters. Hope you can get to this. Thank you.","rating":5,"reviewerName":"wow lots of nicknames","dateAuthorText":"* null * · wow lots of nicknames","moreAction":{"title":"Ratings & Reviews","presentationStyle":[],"actionMetrics":{"$kind":"ActionMetrics","data":[],"custom":{}},"$kind":"flowAction","actionClass":"FlowAction","page":"reviews","pageData":{"shelves":[{"$kind":"Shelf","impressionMetrics":{"fields":{"id":"12","name":"","impressionType":"ratingsDetails","idType":"sequential","impressionIndex":2}},"contentType":"reviews","marker":null,"items":[{"$kind":"Review","id":"11565603987","title":"I love this app but…","date":"2024-08-03T01:08:46.000Z","dateText":"* null *","contents":"Well, when I go into Camera, there is no more make up a.k.a. the fairy, the make up, and stuff. I don’t know if people have been using them badly and that is why you took them off, or it is just a bug. I have been wanting to use them for so long but they’re gone. So, I have been wondering, if you will check it out, or you purposely took them off. Also, a lot of other stuff has been getting taken off. Again, if you can take a look, that would be great, or if you purposely took them off I am perfectly fine with that. Just warning you. Also when for some reason I deleted this app and got it back I look for all my templates and videos I made but they aren’t showing up. I tried everything I signed into my account but it still didn’t work. I am extremely sad because I usually don’t save all my important templates or videos because I don’t want to take up storage but now I don’t even have them. I also read some other reviews and some other people are having this problem. Please get to this problem. It seems that you are ignoring all the reviews if you are not, and you are reading this, please do something about this. Also, whenever I make some certain videos, it says