tures—like Auto Edit and the teleprompter tool—help democratize the production process at a time when video storytelling has never been so vital. ","ageRating":"4+","productDescription":"Detail combines the simplicity of a camera app with the power of a professional AI video editor. Whether you're creating a 60-second reaction video, a polished YouTube vlog, a 30-minute interview or podcast, or going live to thousands of viewers, you can do it all in one place with Detail.\n\n\nINSTANT VIDEO WITH AI AUTO-EDIT\n\nRecord or import a video and let AI Auto-Edit do the rest. Detail's AI finds the best moments, removes silences, and creates ready-to-share shorts and reels automatically. Instant video — record, done.\n\n\nAI DIRECTOR — YOUR PERSONAL TELEPROMPTER\n\nStay on script with AI Director, your conversational teleprompter guide. It listens as you speak and keeps you on track, so every take is your best take. Perfect for content creators, educators, and presenters.\n\n\nMULTICAM RECORDING\n\nTurn your iPhone and iPad into a multi-camera video studio. Record from multiple angles simultaneously and switch between them in real time. Professional multicam production without the professional price tag.\n\n\nREACTION VIDEOS MADE EASY\n\nRecord split-screen reaction videos to any content in seconds. Import a video, hit record, and share your reaction with the world. The fastest way to create reaction content for TikTok, YouTube Shorts, and Instagram Reels.\n\n\nPODCAST & VIDEO PODCAST STUDIO\n\nRecord, edit, and publish professional video podcasts. Detail handles layouts, audio levels, and transitions so you can focus on the conversation. Support for remote guests and multi-camera setups.\n\n\nLIVESTREAMING TO ANY PLATFORM\n\nGo live to YouTube, Twitch, Facebook, or any RTMP destination directly from Detail. Add overlays, switch cameras, and engage your audience — all from your iPhone or iPad.\n\n\nGREEN SCREEN & CHROMA KEY\n\nRemove or replace your background instantly with green screen support. No physical green screen needed — Detail's AI handles background removal automatically.\n\n\nAI AUTO-CAPTIONS & SUBTITLES\n\nAdd accurate auto captions in 50+ languages. Customize fonts, colors, and styles. Captions are fully editable and can be exported as separate subtitle files. Transcribe your content with a single tap.\n\n\nPROFESSIONAL EDITING TOOLS\n\n• Trim, cut, and split clips with precision\n\n• Add text, stickers, and overlays\n\n• Apply filters, effects, and color grading\n\n• Adjust speed — slow motion, time-lapse, and more\n\n• 4K video export for maximum quality\n\n• Music and sound effects library\n\n\nBUILT FOR CONTENT CREATORS\n\nDetail is the all-in-one video editor for UGC creators, vloggers, podcasters, and social media content creators. Create professional content for TikTok, YouTube, Instagram, and every platform — without juggling complicated apps or expensive gear.\n\n\nCLOUD SYNC & COLLABORATION\n\nAccess your projects across all your Apple devices. Collaborate with your team in real time. Your video studio, everywhere you go.\n\n\nDownload Detail today and join millions of creators making better videos with AI.\n\n\nTerms of Use: https://detail.co/terms\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://detail.co/privacy","rating":4.6,"ratingCount":"2.8K","buttonAction":{"title":"Get","presentationStyle":[],"actionMetrics":{"$kind":"ActionMetrics","data":[{"fields":{"actionDetails":{"buyParams":"productType=C&price=0&salableAdamId=1673518618&pricingParameters=STDQ&pg=default&appExtVrsId=885436080"},"location":[{"locationPosition":0,"locationType":"button","name":"Get","idType":"its_id","id":"1673518618","variantId":"default","experimentId":"14318704-6577-4045-8295-40617e09cf41","experimentLocale":"en-US"},{"locationPosition":3,"locationType":"lockup","name":"Detail: AI Video Editor","idType":"its_id","id":"1673518618","variantId":"default","experimentId":"14318704-6577-4045-8295-40617e09cf41","experimentLocale":"en-US"},{"locationPositio